genresAdvancedInfo.name: italian progressive metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Italian progressive metal is a genre that combines the complex rhythms and harmonies of progressive rock with the aggressive energy and technical virtuosity of heavy metal. It often features intricate instrumental passages, unconventional song structures, and thought-provoking lyrics that explore philosophical and existential themes.
